{"tid":611524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴打違例】擔心被票控份外小心 單車友：有啲大石砸死蟹","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T08:47:51.000Z","uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8775e71e0a3b4227494a1e713e494e69478190a","tid":611524,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"警方於今日起一連10日在新界南總區打擊嚴重單車違例事項，其間不作口頭警告，會即時採取檢控，不少踩單車的市民擔心誤墮法網，均顯得特別小心謹慎。市民曾先生認為警方不作警告，即對單車違例事項作檢控，「有啲大石砸死蟹囉，其實唔太清楚點樣違例，應該做多啲宣傳教育先，唔好話一嚟就嚟(檢控)。」<br />\n<br />\n就讀中二的顏同學直指：「知道唔可以戴住耳塞踩單車，過馬路要落車推(單車)。」她又謂：「今日連租車都未租，屋企人就打電話嚟，提醒話警方有執法行動。」<br />\n<br />\n另一名12歲何同學，則一度在單車徑踩滑板，他表示不知道警方有執法行動，又說：「見唔多人先踩一陣（滑板），多人就唔會。」惟他認為警方執法檢控前，「可以先畀警告，唔使咁嚴重，下下都罰！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/140002_a117092344f7cd1d4c00cb0a8522d204.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F140002_a117092344f7cd1d4c00cb0a8522d204.png&h=f400133b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffcdd5c7dafd6580a481d01447cf8eefd9ded393","tid":611524,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"中國人是需要管的"},{"pid":"8a02b2722607b456d8019eedf89f5a71e41b6518","tid":611524,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7f3f40804eb6ce998d55696d14ca9a82565ad9","tid":611524,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a02b2722607b456d8019eedf89f5a71e41b6518","tid":611524,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"顔同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}